  ('medical-tech-moex-20048', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Prothrombin time（PT）檢查所需添加的物質，除Ca2+外，還有下列何者？ Kaolin  Cephalin  Cobalamin  tissue thromboplastin', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 57, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20049', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Thrombotic thrombocytopenic purpura 之實驗室檢驗特徵為： 周邊血液抹片出現紅血球碎片   血漿 D-dimer上升   血小板減少   纖維蛋白裂解產物上升', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 58, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20050', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於血小板的敘述，何者錯誤？ 正常人血小板直徑約1.5～3.5μm 是megakaryocyte的細胞核碎裂形成 dense granules和αgranules是細胞質內的重要構造 canalicular membrane system是血小板與外界溝通之主要管道', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 59, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20051', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列血小板αgranules內蛋白質中，何者是血小板自行合成，非自循環中吸收而來？ fibrinogen  VWF  PDGF  fibronectin', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 60, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20052', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關factor Ⅷ與 VWF的敘述，何者為非？ VWF是factor Ⅷ執行凝血作用時的輔因子  VWF可與factor Ⅷ形成複合體 血中VWF分子量遠大於factor Ⅷ  經thrombin的活化切割，factor Ⅷ才具有功能', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 61, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20053', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是serpin（serine protease inhibitor）？ antithrombin Ⅲ    heparin cofactor Ⅱ PAI-1    TFPI（tissue factor pathway inhibitor）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 62, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20054', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列凝固因子之酵素與其輔因子（cofactor）的配對，正確的是： IX-V   X-Ⅷ    Ⅶ-TF   XII-XI prekallikrein-high molecular weight kininogen（HMWK）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 63, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20055', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於第十因子（factor X）的敘述，下列何者正確？ 是一種serine protease    factor Ⅷ是其輔因子 factor X具有2個kringle domains  factor X作用時，完全不需要phospholipid輔助', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 64, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('medical-tech-moex-20056', 'medical-tech', 'medical-tech-moex-094-9168e375', 'sub-medical-tech-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列關於洗滌紅血球製品的敘述，何者錯誤？ 輸洗滌紅血球不會有傳染肝炎之危險 IgA缺乏病人在輸血時必須使用洗滌紅血球 洗滌紅血球會有細菌污染的危險 使用洗滌紅血球可避免發熱性非溶血性輸血反應之發生', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "96d440809c0b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "bc22c58d926f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "094020", "c": "105", "s": "2001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "臨床血液學與血庫學", "year": "094", "exam_name": "094年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、心理師、呼吸治療師、營養師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 65, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "mt", "db_exam_id": "medical-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
